            <description><![CDATA[<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="16"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078335" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211633242.thumb.jpg" WIDTH="328" HEIGHT="450" /></A></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
帅气儒雅的“四爷”吴奇隆这次要颠覆形象了。昨天，电视剧《向着炮火前进》举行了开机发布会，吴奇隆告诉现场主持人《中国电影报道》主播瑶淼，这次自己将演绎一个不一样的土匪。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="14"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="14"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078337" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211633244.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
当天导演林间中带领主演吴奇隆、甘婷婷、谢孟伟等人以戏装亮相。导演对瑶淼介绍，这部电视剧虽是抗战题材，但拍摄画面明朗色彩鲜亮，剧中各主演造型帅气脱俗，“潮味儿”十足，颇具偶像气质。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="15"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="15"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078338" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211633245.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
其中凭借清宫穿越剧《步步惊心》人气爆增的吴奇隆将在片中一改温文尔雅的形象，出演一个黄埔军校毕业却因政见不和而占山为王的个性英雄雷子枫。吴奇隆对瑶淼笑言，</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">雷子枫性格火爆、有情有义又“有缺陷”，演完该剧后也许会有人叫他“雷爷”。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="18"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078336" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211633243.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="16"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="16"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078335" TARGET="_blank"></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
虽现在对角色十分感兴趣，但吴奇隆对瑶淼说，刚接到剧本时也有些顾虑，“我看过很多抗战剧，人物造型都很土气。虽然我很想转型，但也怕我的八路造型让观众难以接受。没想到造型出来后，我发现这是一部‘潮味儿’十足的戏，我的造型是皮夹克大背头，特别酷。爱情戏又特别浪漫，完全打消了我的顾虑”。他还告诉瑶淼，剧中涉及多处爆破、格斗等危险场景，皆由他“零替身”上阵。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="17"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="17"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078334" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211633241.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
“这是我第一次拍这么苦的戏，因为是战争戏，整天都要待在漫天黄沙的地方，而且有很多爆破戏份，我也会说粗话、动手动脚打人，还得被人打。”“被人打？”听到这里瑶淼不禁疑问，谁忍心打这位如今正当红的“四爷”啊？“因为谢孟伟五岁就开始习武，所以这部戏里最困难、最惊险的对打戏都是他首当其冲，对打的对象也有很多，我是其中经常被打的那位，而且还在里面受了很多折磨。”吴奇隆说道。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="18"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="18"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078336" TARGET="_blank"></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
戏中，曾在《新水浒》和《新亮剑》中有出色表现的甘婷婷出演干练女战士上官于飞，她是留学归来的高级专业人才，主攻密码学，在执行任务时，与雷子枫和王新饰演的八路军军官刘建功相遇，三人产生了一段复杂的感情纠葛。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="19"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="19"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078339" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211633246.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="75"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="75">《向着炮火前进》讲述了雷子枫占山为王，与国共日三方斡旋斗智，他拒绝王新饰演的刘建功的招揽，却在遇见甘婷婷饰演的八路军特派员之后，对其一见倾心，并在其劝导下加入八路军，共同抵御日军侵略的热血故事。</SPAN></P>]]></description>
