        <item>
            <title>赵薇变保姆吃不消 赵又廷成小孩保镖</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4b355d260102dzn5.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="75"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="75"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="14"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078190" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211357181.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="75"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="75">尽管已经升级当了妈妈，但赵薇对付小孩子似乎还是有些经验不足。在电影《爱</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">love</FONT></SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">》的拍摄期间，饰演她儿子的小演员就让她慨叹：“和小孩子演戏真的很辛苦”。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="14"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="14"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078190" TARGET="_blank"></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
电影里的赵薇是一名单身妈妈，除了戏中照顾儿子，拍戏之余她依然恪尽职守，像对待自己女儿那样，把小演员抱在腿上一起玩。拍戏的过程是漫长的，总这么当保姆，赵薇也有吃不消的时候。她偶尔也会抱怨说：“和小孩演戏真的很辛苦。”</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="15"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="15"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078193" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211357184.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
你觉得辛苦？小演员还不耐烦呢！拍戏时间太长，小朋友开始犯困了，赵薇只好再次投入到保姆的工作当中。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="16"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="16"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078192" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211357183.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="79"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="0" SIZSET="79">片中的赵又廷为了追求赵薇，给小朋友当起了临时爸爸。有一天他接孩子放学，正赶上小朋友们吵架。几位小演员相当入戏，竟然假戏真做打出了真火。戏拍完了，还有人想着报仇呢，幸好赵又廷及时发现赶快拦住了。不过，不一会小演员又跌倒了，于是赵保镖再次出动……</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="17"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="17"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078191" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211357182.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
《爱</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">love</FONT></SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">》的导演钮承泽工作认真严格，剧组上下都对他存有三分敬畏，而小演员则是记恨起了他。不让睡觉的是你，要求最多的是你，总说我的也是你。面对投诉，钮承泽还真不敢怎么着！遇到小演员耍大牌，咱自有妙计……</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="18"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'" SIZCACHE="1" SIZSET="18"><a HREF="http://blog.cntv.cn/batch.download.php?aid=2078194" TARGET="_blank"><img BORDER="0" SRC="http://img.blog.cntv.cn/attachments/2012/02/11841056_201202211357185.thumb.jpg" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 17.95pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
